Elijah Overcomer and his family left New Zealand commune Gloriavale in March 2013 . 
  The commune is a secretive Christian community on New Zealand's west coast . 
  The family said living in Gloriavale was like being in a thriller movie like The Village . 
  Elijah and his wife Rosanna left Gloriavale with their three children . 
  The Overcomers said they were 'blown away' by the kindness of New Zealand churches . 
  Gloriavale residents wear blue uniforms and birth control is non-existent . 
 